{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# Lab 2 Bonus: 穿越时空的光谱 (Redshift Correction)\n",
    "\n",
    "在这个 Bonus 任务中，我们将使用 Numpy 插值技术来修复因宇宙膨胀而红移的星系光谱。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import sys\n",
    "import os\n",
    "\n",
    "sys.path.append('src')\n",
    "from spectrum_fix import GalaxySpectrum\n",
    "\n",
    "plt.rcParams['font.size'] = 12\n",
    "plt.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (10, 6)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 读取光谱数据\n",
    "我们有一个模拟的星系光谱，它已经被红移了 $z=0.1$。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "filepath = '../data/galaxy_spectrum.txt'\n",
    "if not os.path.exists(filepath):\n",
    "    print(\"Warning: Data file not found! Generating dummy data for testing...\")\n",
    "    # 生成假数据以便 Notebook 能运行\n",
    "    wave_dummy = np.linspace(3000, 8000, 500)\n",
    "    flux_dummy = np.exp(-((wave_dummy-5000)/50)**2) * 100\n",
    "    os.makedirs('../data', exist_ok=True)\n",
    "    np.savetxt(filepath, np.column_stack((wave_dummy, flux_dummy)))\n",
    "\n",
    "spec = GalaxySpectrum(filepath)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 绘制原始红移光谱\n",
    "plt.plot(spec.wave, spec.flux, 'k-', alpha=0.5, label='Original Observed Spectrum')\n",
    "plt.xlabel('Observed Wavelength ($\\\\AA$)')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('Flux')\n",
    "plt.legend()\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 红移校正：回到静止系\n",
    "\n",
    "我们需要将观测到的波长 $\\lambda_{obs}$ 变换回静止波长 $\\lambda_{rest} = \\lambda_{obs} / (1+z)$。\n",
    "为了便于与其他星系叠加对比，我们需要将所有光谱插值到一个标准的静止波长网格上。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "z = 0.1\n",
    "# 定义标准静止波长网格 (比如 3000A 到 7000A)\n",
    "target_wave = np.linspace(3000, 7000, 1000)\n",
    "\n",
    "try:\n",
    "    # 调用你的函数\n",
    "    flux_linear = spec.rest_frame_linear(z, target_wave)\n",
    "    flux_cubic = spec.rest_frame_cubic(z, target_wave)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 绘图对比\n",
    "    fig, (ax1, ax2) = plt.subplots(2, 1, sharex=True, figsize=(10, 8))\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 上图：光谱对比\n",
    "    ax1.plot(target_wave, flux_linear, 'b--', label='Linear Interpolation')\n",
    "    ax1.plot(target_wave, flux_cubic, 'r-', alpha=0.7, label='Cubic Spline')\n",
    "    ax1.set_ylabel('Flux')\n",
    "    ax1.legend()\n",
    "    ax1.set_title(f'Rest Frame Spectrum (z={z})')\n",
    "    \n",
    "    # 下图：差异分析\n",
    "    # 观察 Cubic Spline 和 Linear 在峰值处的差异\n",
    "    diff = flux_cubic - flux_linear\n",
    "    ax2.plot(target_wave, diff, 'k-', label='Difference (Cubic - Linear)')\n",
    "    ax2.set_xlabel('Rest Wavelength ($\AA$)')\n",
    "    ax2.set_ylabel('Flux Difference')\n",
    "    ax2.legend()\n",
    "    ax2.grid(True, alpha=0.3)\n",
    "    \n",
    "    plt.show()\n",
    "    \n",
    "except NotImplementedError:\n",
    "    print(\"❌ 请先在 src/spectrum_fix.py 中实现插值函数！\")"
   ]
  }
 ],
